{"id":45509,"date":"2024-01-15T10:00:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-15T04:30:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=45509"},"modified":"2023-05-16T10:22:56","modified_gmt":"2023-05-16T04:52:56","slug":"hanging-lights-for-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/hanging-lights-for-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"Your Ultimate Guide To Illuminate Your Bedroom With Stylish Hanging Lights"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Upgrade your bedroom&#8217;s decor game with these 6 lighting tips<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking to add some warmth and style to your bedroom? One of the easiest and more effective ways to elevate the glam quotient is modern hanging lights for bedroom! The right lighting can transform your space whether you prefer a cosy, intimate atmosphere or a bold and statement look.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But with so many designs available, it can be overwhelming to know where to start. Don&#8217;t worry; we&#8217;ve got you covered! This guide will help you with everything you need to know about hanging wall lights for bedroom, from choosing the right type of light to placement tips and safety considerations. Let&#8217;s get started!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Types Of Hanging Ceiling Lights For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Gone are those days when the bedroom lights only called for tube lights. Nowadays, lighting plays a significant part in interior decoration. Different types of hanging lights are available in the market, such as chandeliers, pendant lights, string lights, and more. While decorating your room, you must consider what purpose that light will fulfil in your space. For instance, if it is for only decor purposes, choose a designer chandelier. If you want a stylish version of bedside light, then pendant lights on both sides or one side of your bed works best.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101244\/hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-types.jpg\" alt=\"Hanging lights for bedroom ceiling which suits, consider what purpose that light will fulfil in your space\" class=\"wp-image-45514\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101244\/hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-types.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101244\/hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-types-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101244\/hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-types-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101244\/hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-types-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Chrome-coloured one-sided pendant light<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Bedroom interior design with a bed that fits just right\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180953\/bedroom-interior-design-with-a-bed-that-fits-just-right.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/different-types-of-lights\/\">Different Types Of Lights<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Choose The Right Theme-based Hanging Lights For Bedroom Ceiling\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to hanging lights, style matters! If you are following a theme, it&#8217;s important to choose lights that match the overall decor of your bedroom. Instead of investing in a light fixture that matches the colour, choose lights that complement your furniture and other accessories. For instance, we have followed a Moroccan decor in the bedroom shown in the image below. So, we have installed chunky hanging ceiling lights for bedroom that go well with the overall theme.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101221\/chunky-hanging-ceiling-lights-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Choose hanging ceiling lights that go well with the overall theme of the bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-45510\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101221\/chunky-hanging-ceiling-lights-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101221\/chunky-hanging-ceiling-lights-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101221\/chunky-hanging-ceiling-lights-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101221\/chunky-hanging-ceiling-lights-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Moroccan pendant-style accent lights for bedroom <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Determine The Best Placement For Your Hanging Ball Lights For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Where you hang your lights can greatly impact the overall look and feel of your bedroom. If it is a prominent accent light fixture, it should be hung in the centre of the room as a focal point. Alternatively, pendant lights go well on either side of the bed, like the one we have used in the picture below. These hanging ball lights do wonder against the black wall behind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101226\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Hanging ball lights in the bedroom goes well on either side of the bed\" class=\"wp-image-45511\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101226\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101226\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101226\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101226\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Minimalist pendant lights for a glamorous bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Create An Intimate Ambience With DIY Plug-In Hanging Lights For Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bedroom lights don&#8217;t have to be expensive. Even some string lights can do wonders. All you need is some inspiration to tickle your creative mind. For instance, two strings of bulbs hanging from the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/four-poster-bed-design-ideas\/\">four-poster bed<\/a> have given this space a moody vibe. They work wonderfully as both ambience light and decorative pieces.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101259\/strands-of-hanging-light-bulbs-for-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Four-poster bed adorned with two strands of hanging light bulbs in the bedroom creates a moody atmosphere\" class=\"wp-image-45517\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101259\/strands-of-hanging-light-bulbs-for-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101259\/strands-of-hanging-light-bulbs-for-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101259\/strands-of-hanging-light-bulbs-for-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101259\/strands-of-hanging-light-bulbs-for-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>DIY decorative hanging lights for bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Determine The Sizing And Scaling Of Your Hanging Lights For Bedroom Ceiling<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When selecting lights for your bedroom, measure the ceiling height and consider the room size. As a general thumb rule, smaller rooms should have smaller fixtures, while larger rooms can handle larger fixtures. Choose a fixture about 1\/3 the size of the furniture it&#8217;s hanging above. If you have a low-height ceiling, skip on the chandelier, as it will make the room feel smaller. Instead, use ambience lights and pendant lights that hang low. It would double as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-table-lamps\/\">bedside lamps<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101254\/pendant-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling.jpg\" alt=\"When selecting hanging lights for the bedroom ceiling, consider the room's size and height; use ambient and pendant lights\" class=\"wp-image-45516\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101254\/pendant-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101254\/pendant-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101254\/pendant-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101254\/pendant-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-ceiling-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Sleek, modern pendant lights for grey bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Smart Modern Hanging Lights For Bedroom With Space Crunch<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hanging lights can be a great way to add style and ambience to even the smallest bedrooms. Choose compact, warm-coloured light fixtures with high lumens. Use multiple light sources, position them according to function and maximise natural light with large windows. Add accent lighting and dimmers, and avoid harsh overhead lighting for a cosy ambience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101250\/modern-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-with-high-lumens.jpg\" alt=\"Modern hanging lights for bedroom with high lumens add style and ambience\" class=\"wp-image-45515\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101250\/modern-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-with-high-lumens.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101250\/modern-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-with-high-lumens-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101250\/modern-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-with-high-lumens-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101250\/modern-hanging-lights-for-bedroom-with-high-lumens-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Sleek, intricate light fixtures for small bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Take Good Care Of Your Hanging Ball Lights For Bedroom\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your light fixtures are hung, taking care of them is essential to ensure they last for years. If you have metallic light fixtures, polish them every six months to keep them shining. Also, it&#8217;s important to keep replacing the bulbs and get the wiring and earthing checked regularly to prevent damage. Since you have spent a fortune decorating your bedroom with stylish light fixtures, you must take good care of them to ensure they shine for long.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101233\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-maintain.jpg\" alt=\"Maintain hanging ball lights for the bedroom for longevity- tips for care and cleaning\" class=\"wp-image-45512\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101233\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-maintain.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101233\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-maintain-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101233\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-maintain-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/16101233\/hanging-ball-lights-for-bedroom-maintain-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Golden-hued globe chandelier for bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bedroom is the most personal space for every individual. So, its design should reflect your personality and taste. We hope this guide on hanging lights for bedroom was beneficial to you. If you need help designing a stunning bedroom, feel free to book a free consultation. Explore <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/\">our blog section<\/a> for more incredible bedroom design ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Looking to upgrade your bedrooms interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15143526\/looking-to-upgrade-your-bedrooms-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQ about hanging lights in the bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. Can hanging lights be used as the primary source of lighting in a bedroom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Absolutely, yes! With proper wattage bulbs and enough lights, you won&#8217;t need overhead tube lights.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. What is the ideal height for hanging lights in a bedroom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The ideal height for hanging lights in a bedroom depends on the type of fixture and the ceiling height. As a general rule, chandeliers or large pendant lights should be hung at least 7 feet above the floor. Smaller pendant lights ideally should be around 24-30 inches above the nightstand or tabletop for comfortable reading or tasks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. What safety measures should you keep in mind while installing hanging lights in your bedroom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Use appropriate fixtures and wiring<\/li><li>Turn off power before installation<\/li><li>Secure fixture with the proper hardware<\/li><li>Keep away from flammable materials<\/li><li>Follow instructions and consider hiring a professional<\/li><li>Regularly check for wear or damage and replace faulty parts.<\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n